						               													<description>Accurate and easy to play, Glory days College Football brings the big time Saturday afternoon excitement to your table top.  GDCF employs a unique system, Trench Control, to help determine how well each team will perform on any given play.  Just like real life, penalties, turnovers and big plays can add an element of excitement to your game.  Choose from all-time great teams or from season sets.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are three ways to play the game.  You can play the game entirely in Play-By-Play mode which takes about 90 minutes.  You can play Simulated Drive mode where you simulate the gist of every drive for an abbreviated version which lasts about 30 minutes.  Or you can play a hybrid mode where you can speed through the first half of each drive and grind it in from there.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game is available in pdf format at this time.  You get the rulebook, charts, and 30 all time great college football teams from which to choose.  All you will need is the ability to print the materials, two d10, 2d6 and a d20.  More team sets will become available in the future so be on the lookout for that.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
